Package: python-vplants.plantgl
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Provides: ${python:Provides}
Description: PlantGL package for OpenAlea and VPlants.
 Plant Geometric Library is a powerfull library to create and display vegetal 3D scene.
 It provides a scene graph, a set of geometric objects such as primitives, 
 mesh, nurbs, and specific objects (e.g. swung, asymetric hulls) used to 
 represent plants. A 3D viewer is also provided.
